Package: assignment4shinykkapoor
Title: Interactive Data Exploration Tools for ETC5523
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Kunal", "Kapoor", email = "kkap011@student.monash.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package was developed as part of the ETC5523 Communicating with Data unit at Monash University. It provides tools for exploring and visualizing a selected dataset in an interactive and reproducible way, including cleaned data, functions for exploration and summary, an interactive Shiny app, and a pkgdown website for documentation.
